Extract ALL text from the title block and every general note on this drawing. Include every field without exception:
- Part number, part name, drawing number, revision level
- Material specification (alloy, grade, condition/temper, standard e.g. AMS/ASTM/EN)
- General tolerances: linear (e.g. ±0.1 for 2-place decimals), angular
- Surface finish: general Ra/Rz callout, any surface texture symbols in the title block
- Heat treatment, case hardening depth, hardness requirements (HRC/HB/HV)
- Plating, coating, anodising, painting specifications
- Weight, scale, sheet size, number of sheets
- Projection standard (first-angle / third-angle / ISO / ASME)
- Drawing standard (ASME Y14.5, ISO 1101, BS 8888, etc.)
- Fits and limits notation if stated in the title block or notes (e.g. H7/g6)
- Datum reference frame callouts if defined in the title block
- Approved materials list note or restricted materials callout
- Every numbered or lettered note on the drawing, verbatim
Zoom in to read fine print. Return all text verbatim, organised by section, as a single string in the "text" field.
